  "texts": [
    "This score was significantly lower than the score for questions without images (p < 0.001).",
    "Of all answerable questions, 62.3% were answered correctly.",
    "For questions without images, the annual rates of correct answers ranged from 56.3% to 78.8% (Table 1).",
    "Moreover, the accuracy rate for scenario-based questions without images was 69.1%, which was higher than the rate for standalone questions (62.1%), although the difference was not significant (p = 0.06) (Table 2).",
    "Each question was asked twice, and 72.5% elicited the same responses after 2 repetitions."
